      "module_path": "tddd::catalogue_to_extended_crate_codec",
      "docs": "Stateless codec converting CatalogueDocument to ExtendedCrate (TypeGraph A). Modified in this track: (1) validate_supported_bound private method is removed and the codec now accepts all syn-parseable bound strings without rejection (ADR D1 / IN-02); (2) rustdoc impl-block and trait-declaration level generics are placed into the correct catalogue fields (ADR D2 / IN-09); (3) when TraitImplDeclV2.for_ is Some, the fully-qualified path is parsed to determine external-crate membership and register external_crates and paths accordingly; when for_ is None the parent TypeEntry type is used as before (ADR D4 / IN-13). The public shape (unit_struct + encode via port) is unchanged.",
