      "module_path": "tddd::signal_evaluator_v2",
      "docs": "Stateless secondary adapter implementing SignalEvaluatorPort. Modified in this track by five changes: (1) strip_outlives_from_index removed and fingerprint generation updated for {lhs, rhs, operator} structure (ADR D1 / IN-03 / IN-04); (2) symmetric comparison logic added for impl-block and trait-declaration generics (InherentImplDeclV2.impl_generics / TraitImplDeclV2.impl_generics / TraitEntry.generics vs rustdoc counterparts) (ADR D2 / IN-09); (3) a_id_remap Pre-step added to Phase 1 builder (ADR D3 / IN-10); (4) patch_impl_for_ids and patch_impl_trait_ids deleted from Phase 1 (ADR D3 / IN-11); (5) C-side build_impl_identity_map for_is_external filter removed so cross-crate impls are included in c_impls; B-side orphan impl insertion is unchanged (already inserts all impls without filter), so both sides now contain cross-crate impls symmetrically (ADR D4 / IN-13). The public shape (unit_struct + evaluate via port) is unchanged.",
